{
  "stem": "11998.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think I should talk about the-- what the Nazis did and how they lulled us into a false sense of security and that they would not bother us.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Right after my father came back from Russia in 1940, the Jewish community organized itself.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the man who was in charge of the Judenrein was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he felt that as long as the Jews cooperated with the Germans, that they would be able-- that they would leave them alone.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the first thing they came, and they asked like they asked everywhere else, to give them the silver and the gold and the silver plate and whatever we possessed of value.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That we should give it to them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This would appease them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They would leave us alone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You said the Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What was the Judenrat?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Judenrat was a Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sometimes it was instigated by the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think this one was too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they chose, or somebody chose themselves, to become the spokesman for the town of the Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they would look after welfare, and they would look after hospitalization and generally deal as an intermediary between the Nazi regime and the Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in our town, Sosnoweic-Bedzin-- it was twin sister cities-- [NON-ENGLISH] was very much convinced that he could save a large number of Jews from deportation, or from whatever, and to provide us with a certain amount of economic stability.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he-- I guess the Nazis came to him they said they need 400 men to go to the war camp in Germany.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my father was related through my mother's aunt to [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So it was sort of a loose family connection.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he knew of my father, and my father was a big man, strong man.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
